commit_message: Allow AbstractVector{Record}s as arguments to write
parent(::AbstractVector{Gene}) now checks that all genes have the same parent, and errors if they do not
Updated setproperty! so that it works even if genedata is empty
Export GTF, EMBL, and feature accessor functions
Fixed bug caused by trailing spaces in the last line of a Record
sequence(gene) now returns a LongSubSeq when possible
Print multiple lines for multi-exon genes
Updated sequence(...) to handle join/order loci
Fixed bug when calculating gene lengths with join()

Fixed bug when calculating gene lengths with join()
Fixed bug when calculating gene lengths with join()
Changed iscomplete() to allow ribosomal_slippage but not partial

Merge pull request #10 from hsianktin/master

bugfix for delete!(genes)
Added julia v1.8 and v1.9 to travis
Added reader writer for the EMBL file format

Merge pull request #6 from kdyrhage/interface

Changing the read/write interface to mirror other BioJulia packages.
Allow passing file paths to readgbk/readgff

Merge pull request #4 from kdyrhage/parsegff

Added GFF parser/writer, which allows for converting between GBK and GFF.
